appeared to go out as it was between prisms, only to fl ash again as the light went through the next bulls-eye prism and so on.";}s:42:"_about_page_repeating_content_1_about-body";a:1:{i:0;s:19:"field_59ff8ed4bdb2b";}s:42:"about_page_repeating_content_0_about-title";a:1:{i:0;s:27:"A little bit of informaiton";}s:43:"_about_page_repeating_content_0_about-title";a:1:{i:0;s:19:"field_59ff8eb7bdb2a";}s:42:"about_page_repeating_content_1_about-title";a:1:{i:0;s:12:"Achievements";}s:43:"_about_page_repeating_content_1_about-title";a:1:{i:0;s:19:"field_59ff8eb7bdb2a";}s:42:"about_page_repeating_content_2_about-image";a:1:{i:0;s:3:"176";}s:43:"_about_page_repeating_content_2_about-image";a:1:{i:0;s:19:"field_59ff8f0ebdb2d";}s:42:"about_page_repeating_content_2_about-title";a:1:{i:0;s:21:"Saving the Lighthouse";}s:43:"_about_page_repeating_content_2_about-title";a:1:{i:0;s:19:"field_59ff8eb7bdb2a";}s:41:"about_page_repeating_content_2_about-body";a:1:{i:0;s:1097:"Sea Girt Lighthouse. at Ocean Avenue and Beacon Boulevard in Sea Girt. New Jersey, flashed its first light December 10. 1896. The beacon. which could be seen 15 miles at sea. guided countless mari­ners in their journeys and contributed to the state's economic growth and helped make sailing through local waters safer.

The lighthouse was built to illuminate a blind spot midway in the 38½-mile stretch between Navesink Lighthouse (Twin Lights) to the north and Barnegat Lighthouse to the south. It also served as a land­mark for near by Sea Girt In let and Wreck Pond.

By the early 1900s. there were some 40 light stations - lighthouses. lightships and range lights - along New Jersey's 130-mile coastline. Just over half of them survive. But only 11 of the original lighthouses. including Sea Girt. are open to the public

There are also photos of bygone Sea Girt, including the Third Avenue trolley, Civil-War-era cannons on the Camp Sea Girt beach, the Stockton Hotel, the Tremont Hotel, the old pavilion, vacationers camped under the pines and Big Sea Day celebrations at the beach.";}s:42:"_about_page_repeating_content_2_about-body";a:1:{i:0;s:19:"field_59ff8ed4bdb2b";}s:42:"about_page_repeating_content_3_about-image";a:1:{i:0;s:3:"177";}s:43:"_about_page_repeating_content_3_about-image";a:1:{i:0;s:19:"field_59ff8f0ebdb2d";}s:42:"about_page_repeating_content_3_about-title";a:1:{i:0;s:16:"Visitors Welcome";}s:43:"_about_page_repeating_content_3_about-title";a:1:{i:0;s:19:"field_59ff8eb7bdb2a";}s:41:"about_page_repeating_content_3_about-body";a:1:{i:0;s:394:"Why not visit us? See our <a href="contact.html">contact page </a>for directions. For additional information, you may call 732-974-0514. Or write the Sea Girt Lighthouse Citizens Committee, P.O. Box 83 Sea Girt, NJ 08750.

And please tell your friends about the lighthouse and our web site where you can always find the latest Sea Girt Lighthouse news. We hope to see you at the lighthouse.";}s:42:"_about_page_repeating_content_3_about-body";a:1:{i:0;s:19:"field_59ff8ed4bdb2b";}s:42:"about_page_repeating_content_4_about-image";a:1:{i:0;s:3:"173";}s:43:"_about_page_repeating_content_4_about-image";a:1:{i:0;s:19:"field_59ff8f0ebdb2d";}s:42:"about_page_repeating_content_4_about-title";a:1:{i:0;s:22:"Preserving Our History";}s:43:"_about_page_repeating_content_4_about-title";a:1:{i:0;s:19:"field_59ff8eb7bdb2a";}s:41:"about_page_repeating_content_4_about-body";a:1:{i:0;s:633:"At the conclusion of tours, guests are invited to visit the gift table on the first floor where lighthouse souvenirs and gift items are available for purchase. Items include scale models of the lighthouse, embroidered shirts and caps with the lighthouse logo, postcards and stationery, books, signed, numbered limited-edition prints of the 2010 lighthouse poster and prints of watercolors of the lighthouse painted by area artists.

All proceeds from the sale of merchandise go to fund the operation of the lighthouse, which is run by the Sea Girt Lighthouse Citizens Committee, an all-volunteer, tax-exempt, non-profit foundation.";}s:42:"_about_page_repeating_content_4_about-body";a:1:{i:0;s:19:"field_59ff8ed4bdb2b";}s:13:"about_heading";a:1:{i:0;s:8:"ABOUT US";}s:14:"_about_heading";a:1:{i:0;s:19:"field_5a0473bc1308f";}s:13:"opt_in_header";a:1:{i:0;s:4:"TEST";}s:14:"_opt_in_header";a:1:{i:0;s:19:"field_5a1d944e9f0f7";}}}